Package: cbSCRIP
Title: Case-Base Sampling for Sparse Competing Risk Prediction
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Javier", "Martinez-Rodriguez", email = "javier.mr@stat.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Nirupama", "Tamvada", role = "aut"),
      person("Sahir", "Bhatnagar", role = "aut"),
      person("Gabriela V.", "Cohen Freue", email = "gcohen@stat.ubc.ca", role = c("aut")))
Description: Implements an estimator based on case-base sampling for sparse competing risk prediction, cbSCRIP. It uses an elastic-net penalized multinomial approach with an offset parameter, enabling both accurate prediction and variable selection under competing risks.
